This is a modified version of the Textpattern plugin aks_cache (http://textpattern.org.ua/plugins/aks_cache) that allows you to store cache in the database or files.

To install, grab the current version of the compressed plugin (aks_cache.txt) and paste into the plugin field in Textpattern.

After this plugin will be installed and activated, you ready to go.

It tested with 4.2.0 only.